sentences: Joaquín Riquelme García (born in Murcia, Spain in 1983), is a Spanish viola soloist and member of the Berlin Philharmonic.
Born in Murcia (Spain) in 1983, Joaquín started his music studies in Murcia, before moving to Madrid to study at the Madrid Royal Conservatory.
At 23 he was made joint principal viola of the Barcelona Symphony and Catalonia National Orchestra and in March 2010 he became a full member of the Berlin Philharmonic.
